<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4590563>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Maraura macracantha (Smirnov and Timms, 1983) from Lake Numalla, Queensland, Australia collected by B. V. Timms in April 2002. Parthenogenetic female: (A, B) head pores; (C, D) labrum; (E) antennule; (F) limb I; (G) outer and inner distal lobes of limb I; (H) limb II; (I) exopodite of limb II; (J) exopodite and endites of limb III; (K) soft setae and gnathobase of limb III; (L) exopodite of limb IV; (M) inner portion of limb IV; N, limb V. IDL, inner distal lobe; ODL, outer distal lobe; e1–3, endites of limb I; ep, epipodites; s, sensillae. Scale bar: 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4590563/files/figure.png" .

